------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
JWT token -> jwt.io -> abc.def.ghi
1. header -> encode(type=jwt   alg=hs256)
2. payload -> encode(body)
3. signature -> hmacsha256(secret  ,encode(header)+"."+encode(payload))

