OAuth2.0
console.cloud.google.com
developers.google.com/oauthplayground
scope = https://www.googleapis.com/auth/userinfo.email

1. login with google
2. google login page (client id, scope)
3. login to google
4. concent screen
5. authorization code to leetcode/myApp
6. frondend receives authCode
7. frontend -(authCode)-> backend
8. backend -(authCode,secretKey)-> google
9. backend receives access token
10. backend validate access token
11. backend validate token, grant access to user
